{
  "stem": "3973.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they settled in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They survived, all three of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And finally, through my sister, and there was still mail going on, we realized that all of us are alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So in spite of the fact that I left them, and given them-- I've given them up entirely for dead.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were alive, but I had no feelings for them at that point.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Interesting, when the first winter of 1942 approached, most of the people who were brought to the camp were brought in the summer time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They had no winter clothing or anything like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So the-- the camp civilians had arranged that they would send the people to the place where they came from, wherever they had possessions, to bring some winter clothing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I went with my brother and my uncle to the village.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But first of all, we stopped in Bochnia to see my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then we went to the village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had some adventures there, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were arrested and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But finally, we got a lot of our possessions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Not only for ourselves, but also for things that were-- then we, again, went to the parents and left them there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now, at that point, as I said, the camp was not run by the military.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I could have escaped and stayed there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't want to, because I said I can-- my-- I have a better chance of surviving in the camp than you are, where you were in a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And this was ghetto B.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "This was the part of the ghetto which was usually older people or sick people, who don't work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They usually were the first victims.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
